Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after the execution of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total waiting time to the SW-Checklist Completed following SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Average time until SW-Checklist Completed is performed after SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in variants that lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all process variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases where the subsequent activity is Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission occurs

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in comparison with the time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after the execution of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in long-running variants (performance > 1,000,000 seconds)
Metric: the average of the function base > 1000000 where base is the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants involving reviewer assignment challenges
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Minimum time until SW-Awaiting AE Assignment is performed after SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days in delayed checklist completion paths
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days'
